author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | The Jonathan Ross Show
text: Wossy returns for a brand new series of his chat show as he welcomes a new batch of celebrity guests. Joining him tonight will be Vin Diesel, star of the upcoming movie release The Last Witch Hunter, and Olympic and world champion Jessica Ennis-Hill, who will no doubt be discussing her plans to defend her heptathlon at Rio 2016. Longstanding comedy duo Harry Enfield and Paul Whitehouse will also be along to no doubt provide some laughs and to chat about their upcoming Legends! Live Tour. Speaking of legends, Mr Tom Jones will be on to talk about what he's been up to and to sing a song or two. No doubt himself and Jonathan will have plenty to bond over backstage given both their dealings with the BBC...
